{"type": "article", "id": 29498, "title": "男装品牌开的咖啡馆，亮点是用得恰到好处的迷人插画", "description": "漫画真是表达轻松闲适的好手法。", "date": "2016-07-12T23:02:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6400, "name": "咖啡店"}, {"id": 30104, "name": "Tailor’s coffee"}, {"id": 30105, "name": "Pelikamo"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 268, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712174211BgszDIenH9kMa4up.png", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>瑞士苏黎世新开了一家咖啡馆，从玻璃窗前路过，能看到一个手捧咖啡、微微躬身、面带微笑的卡通服务生，然而他穿的并不是服务生一样的黑色西服，而是在深色毛衣外加了一件卡其色的夹克。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174332ZVSfU7ELFueA3bpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174536Dc6LT3AHaY0mnibu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751753\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>店中每一个咖啡杯上都有这样的卡通小人，他们的穿着打扮或者携带的物件都不一样。一个留着络腮胡、戴着圆框眼镜的男子夹着画走过，他穿着黄色的格子外套和黑色的长裤，就像一位严谨保守教书先生。一个长着鹰鼻的男子捧着两本书，交叉着腿站在那里，那条绿色的长裤让他看起来闲散自由，更像是一个学生。你也许会奇怪那个带着冲浪板的人，因为他同样穿着蓝色西服白色长裤，而不是海滩边应有的打扮，让他看起来像一个冲浪板推销员而不是去度假的人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175127UFaJM3lGjX7poC5V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174405RaVswyobg5X7Oxp8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174405549AXWOq3YlTRJEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174405idSZHGBLD8QxMuvo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174405AtYRWe8rEgOmzTLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607121748313VYkij8HcouyUhrq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174832EN3bJ8fLMcmtql6O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174627zKHFgxVR0QEs4Lq9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174628KRGONXSQ7gldhi2s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174628fGt4V190nPiyqukb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>所以，这些人物的共同点是都穿着外套和长裤的男士，多看几个之后，你会不自觉注意到他们的衣服。这就是这家店的所有者男装品牌&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.pelikamo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pelikamo</a>&nbsp;的目的，他们在实体店附近开了一家咖啡馆<a href=\"http://www.tailorscoffee.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Tailor’s coffee</a>，并邀请 Instagram 上擅长人物画的插画师&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mr.slowboy/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">mr.slowboy</a>&nbsp;设计包装。所有的人物原型是 Pelikamo 的工作人员，当你在咖啡馆里买了这样一杯咖啡，至少会对服装店产生印象，在对号入座的同时，也会产生一些穿搭的想法。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175651hlqaAF4GTtC3nZce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175650DkTo8KxF4qZnPujJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175654Ox6tzQ4XCj5n2oVG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><p>这样的咖啡小人出现在杯子、糖包、餐盒等物品上，连在一起可以组成了具有欧洲风情的图景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174708Ijk8RgzVBcJAW4ad.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.392578\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175059Bj8OeyMA254ktNJu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.484000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712174741agqKUOmpe8IQsSMY.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.426257\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pelikamo.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pelikamo</a>&nbsp;网站</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175245dGlQszZcAIrHea7W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pelikamo.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pelikamo</a>&nbsp;实体店</div></figcaption></figure></div><p>Mr.slowboy 在 Instagram上贴了不少自己画的人物画，有布什总统、英国女王，也有街头巷尾的小人物和自己的日常生活。而将插画用于商业也不是&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.pelikamo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pelikamo</a>&nbsp;第一个想到，还有英国帽子店 lockhatters 找他合作，mr.slowboy 笔下浓郁的英伦风情搭配在店铺中充满别样的时尚。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175417RBQdAYKnDXz4yVea.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.986486\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;lockhatters&nbsp;</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175232Nf945RuVFnpPgAiq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673378\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175417tjW5ZJu6Elw9XQPh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.152305\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175431hB0mgKQDaTswVAqo.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.559055\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712175433cbazphNUgALHuEmW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.257642\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.everydayobject.us/2016/07/11/tailors-coffee/\" rel=\"nofollow\">everydayobject</a>、<a href=\"http://www.pelikamo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pelikamo</a>、<a href=\"http://www.tailorscoffee.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tailor’s coffee</a></p>"}